{"tid":1253254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫護法律界：5示威者醫院內被捕 4人涉暴動罪","createTime":"2019-06-23T12:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T16:18:17.000Z","uid":167451,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a9336ec0196b4178d7e2a752c9316f8880c629f7","tid":1253254,"uid":167451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:55:45.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】政府條訂逃犯條例引起嚴重衝突，近日醫管局亦證實有傷者在求醫期間遭警方拘捕。醫學界、衞生服務界及法律界舉行聯合記者會，整合民陣、星火同盟等資料，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">透露有5人在公立醫院求醫期間被捕，4人涉暴動罪、1人涉非法集結罪。若以醫院劃分，3人來自伊利沙伯醫院，來自廣華醫院及仁濟醫院各1人。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n衞生服務界選委洪梓然表示，有前線護士向他透露，有並無攜帶委任證的警員，到醫院恐嚇醫護人員以索取資料。但基於保護護士情況下，不能透露更多詳情，包括該名護士所工作的醫院，以及相關恐嚇內容。<br />\n<br />\n公立醫院醫生、醫學界選委黃任匡重申，「醫生及護士的專業守則均列明，除非徵得病人同意，否則不會向第三者披露任何資料，醫護人員亦沒有責任提供資料。」他強調警方應用正常途徑，向法庭申請手令，然後向醫院正式書面申請醫療報告。<br />\n<br />\n對於疑有警員在醫院向醫護人員索取病人個人資料，執業大律師兼法政匯思召集人吳宗鑾指，非法搜證下取得的證據，在法庭上有機會影響證據的呈堂性。<br />\n<br />\n黃任匡澄清，「醫護人員的工作不包括主動報警，即使面對家暴受害者，我們只是鼓勵對方報警，而非主動報警，病人有其自主權。」他又指「現時在社會上製造恐怖，讓傷者不敢求醫。」並認為醫管局應發出更清晰的指引和訊息，包括讓醫護人員在受到壓力下，知道如何恪守專業守則，不透露病人資料；同時讓外界市民知道，醫護人員除了提供救援服務，都會盡最大能力保護他們的資料。<br />\n<br />\nSource:- <a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E7%95%8C-5%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E5%85%A7%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-4%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%89%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA-100000814.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E7%2595%258C-5%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA-100000814.html&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr1ybpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=b4bf8436\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E7%95%8C-5%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E5%85%A7%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-4%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%89%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA-100000814.html</a><br />\n<br />\n醫管局好似無話咁多 cases<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家玩到醫院都做假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> HK is dying"},{"pid":"0735e83e9c288b90acf2b6230abe6358375efc45","tid":1253254,"uid":167451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:59:12.000Z","msg":"香港還是以前的香港嗎"},{"pid":"2ba58d104911fb6daaf77561d9b39daf23cce6a5","tid":1253254,"uid":14520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:23:14.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死黑警，推"},{"pid":"546201925203c7ee183bdae0175fd755251e3ac7","tid":1253254,"uid":56023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:26:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d775b76e049074dfbacf01579e63a8f3ee18872","tid":1253254,"uid":164761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:32:36.000Z","msg":"pk"},{"pid":"79a9911258375cf9ebfe4a2fa90b409e28bafab4","tid":1253254,"uid":263657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:34:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"633714c8d25ff455576a68245d7df8c974b068f9","tid":1253254,"uid":167451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T15:40:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0b631def374cf78611b81ccdf8dfc0d0fa25a1","tid":1253254,"uid":49695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:13:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"51d70d11c0eb2b0faf26dcfed53616eb9c9ea6a2","tid":1253254,"uid":167451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"